Name: Number of concepts
Description: Number of senses linked to Concepticon

Name: colexification of SKIN and BARK
Description:
Computes if two concepts are expressed with the same form in a language (i.e. if they are
colexified).
Feature_Spec: {"id": "SkinAndBark", "name": "colexification of SKIN and BARK", "function": {"class": "cltoolkit.features.lexicon.Colexification", "args": ["SKIN", "BARK"], "kwargs": {"ablist": null, "alabel": null, "blabel": null}}, "type": "bool", "note": null, "categories": {"null": "missing data", "true": "colexifies S, K, I, N and B, A, R, K", "false": "does not colexify S, K, I, N and B, A, R, K"}, "requires": ["cltoolkit.features.reqs.concepts"]}
